parameters.name: session_id
parameters.description: Partner ID is assigned upon registration is successful

parameters.name: action_date
parameters.description: The time in AUT system, need to strictly synchronize to prevent record mismatches

parameters.name: sign
parameters.description: Digital signature (Generated as shown in doc)

response_fields.name: code
response_fields.description: Image error test in full step, Empty is no error happened

response_fields.name: message
response_fields.description: Image error details if there are step errors

response_fields.name: result_id
response_fields.description: The identifier for up API request by each step

response_fields.name: file_paths
response_fields.description: Path information can be used for

response_fields.name: step_no
response_fields.description: The step of the face in the complete key of control results

response_fields.name: error
response_fields.description: Name of the face in your language

response_fields.name: image_id
response_fields.description: The image id of this step

response_fields.name: user_data
response_fields.description: The image hash code representing the contents

response_fields.name: control_flag
response_fields.description: The control end at the face in the being condition

response_fields.name: original_price
response_fields.description: The original price of the face in the being

notes: This appears to be an API for video/image scanning with facial analysis capabilities. The documentation includes error codes and response fields related to step-by-step processing of images/video.
